[1mInstallation[0m

[4mBuild from source[0m

[4mPrerequisites[0m

 [33m•[0m gcc/clang (C++14-compatible)
 [33m•[0m libpcre2
 [33m•[0m sqlite ≥ 3.9.0
 [33m•[0m zlib, bz2
 [33m•[0m libcurl ≥ 7.23.0
 [33m•[0m libarchive
 [33m•[0m libunistring
 [33m•[0m wireshark ([37m[40m tshark [0m, for pcap support)
 [33m•[0m cargo/rust (for PRQL compiler)

[4mBuild[0m

 ▌[33m[40m$ [0m[37m[40m./autogen.sh    # only needed when building from a git clone    [0m
 ▌[33m[40m$ [0m[37m[40m./configure                                                     [0m
 ▌[33m[40m$ [0m[37m[40mmake                                                            [0m
 ▌[33m[40m$ [0m[37m[40msudo make install                                               [0m

[1mUsage[0m

 ▌[33m[40m$ [0m[37m[40mlnav /path/to/file1 /path/to/dir ...             [0m
 ▌[33m[40m$ [0m[37m[40mlnav --ioc /path/to/ioc.txt /var/log/auth.log    [0m

See the ]8;;https://docs.lnav.org\[4mupstream documentation[0m]8;;\¹ for full usage details.

 [34m▌[0m[1] - https://docs.lnav.org 

[4mUsage with [0m[4m[37m[40m systemd-journald [0m

 ▌[33m[40m$ [0m[37m[40mjournalctl [0m[37m[40m|[0m[37m[40m lnav                                                                       [0m
 ▌[33m[40m$ [0m[37m[40mjournalctl -f [0m[37m[40m|[0m[37m[40m lnav                                                                    [0m
 ▌[33m[40m$ [0m[37m[40mjournalctl -o short-iso [0m[37m[40m|[0m[37m[40m lnav   # include year in timestamps                           [0m
 ▌[33m[40m$ [0m[37m[40mjournalctl -o json [0m[37m[40m|[0m[37m[40m lnav        # structured fields (PRIORITY, _SYSTEMD_UNIT, etc.)    [0m

